# VGA STORE BACKEND (SPRING BOOT)

## 📌 1. Giới thiệu

Dự án backend cho website bán VGA, sử dụng Spring Boot.

---

## 📊 2. ERD (Tóm tắt)

* USERS (1) —— (N) ORDERS

* ORDERS (1) —— (N) ORDER_ITEMS

* PRODUCTS (1) —— (N) ORDER_ITEMS

* USERS (1) —— (1) CART

* CART (1) —— (N) CART_ITEMS

* PRODUCTS (1) —— (N) CART_ITEMS

---

## 🧠 3. Giải thích

* ORDER_ITEMS: lưu chi tiết đơn hàng (product, quantity, price)
* CART_ITEMS: lưu sản phẩm trong giỏ hàng

---

## 🗄️ 4. Lược đồ quan hệ (Relational Schema)

### USERS

* USERS(
  id PRIMARY KEY,
  username,
  password,
  email,
  role
)

### PRODUCTS

* PRODUCTS(
  id PRIMARY KEY,
  name,
  brand_id,
  price,
  stock,
  description,
  img_url,
  FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES BRANDS(id)
)

### BRAND
* BRANDS(
  id PRIMARY KEY,
  name
)

### ORDERS

* ORDERS(
  id PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id,
  total_price,
  status,
  FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES USERS(id)
)

### ORDER_ITEMS

* ORDER_ITEMS(
  id PRIMARY KEY,
  order_id,
  product_id,
  quantity,
  price,
  FOREIGN KEY (order_id) REFERENCES ORDERS(id),
  FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES PRODUCTS(id)
)

### CART

* CART(
  id PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id,
  FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES USERS(id)
)

### CART_ITEMS

* CART_ITEMS(
  id PRIMARY KEY,
  cart_id,
  product_id,
  quantity,
  FOREIGN KEY (cart_id) REFERENCES CART(id),
  FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES PRODUCTS(id)
)

